install_msg: Thanks for installing, I hope you enjoy :) To stay up to date with breaking changes, you might want to join my Support Discord. To find documentation, Discord, and more, drop by the website at <https://coffeebank.github.io/coffee-cogs/jadict>
name: jadict
description: Japanese dictionary bot. Searches Jisho using Jisho API. Includes alternate links to Wiktionary, DeepL, and Google Translate.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any End User Data.
